This option is used to record whether the methods of classes related to the BCI(ByteCode Instrumentation) operation at the agent are operated properly.
When creating an object of a class, this option records the start and end of the method using java.lang.reflect.Proxy.

For the target created through the [debug_dump](./agentHelp?key=debug_dump&type=1) option, you can refer to the [debug_class](./agentHelp?key=debug_class&type=1) option.

** As this option may cause performance problems, it should be used for debugging purposes.**

